OWAYEYISIKHULU sakwa-Passenger Rail Agency of South Africa (Prasa), uMnuz  Lucky Montana, uzivikele ngokuthi kungani enemizi yezigidi wabe esebhekana ngqo nomholi wofakazi kwikhomishini ephenya ngokulawulwa koMbuso yidlanzana. Ephendula umbuzo ngemizi yakhe ebiza u-R37 million uMontana, uthe akahambisani nendlela umholi wofakzi u-Advocate Vas Soni, amphonsa ngayo imibuzo. UMontana utshele uSihlalo wekhomishini iJaji Raymond Zondo ukuthi ikhomishini kumele ixolise kuyena. “Uyabona nje ikhomishini kumele ixolise kimina sihlalo. Ngize lana ukuzophendula ezweni. Ikhomishini kumele ingibuze ngezinto engazenza, okubalwa nendaba yezindawo zami. Sihlalo ngikhiphe izincwadi ezifungelwe ezingamakhasi angu-15 mayelana nendawo yami yokuhlala. Ngakho angibaleki,” kusho uMontana. Umphenyi wekhomishini uMnuz Clint Oellerman, uveze ukuthi phakathi kuka-Agasti no-Okthoba 2014, uMontana ubelungiselela ukuthenga imizi emithathu elinganiselwa ku- R36 million. UMontana ukuphikile ukuthi wathenga le mizi esebenzisa imali yakwaPrasa. Ukuphikile ukuthi wagwazelwa. Ngokobufakazi buka-Oellerman's,  ukuthengwa kwale mizi kwenziwa kusetshenziswa ummeli uMnuz Adriaan van der Walt, weSiyangena Technologies. ISiyangena Technologies, kwatholwa ukuthi yathola amathenda ezigidigidi okuhlinzeka ngezokuphepha kwa-Prasa ngokungafanele phakathi kuka-2010 ngesikhathi seNdebe yoMhlaba. Lokhu kwakubandakanya ama-CCTV, ukukhanyisa, ezokuxhumana ngenkontileka ka-R6 billion. UMontana uthe lokhu kungamanga ngoba ulwazi oluvela ezigebengwini, wathi ufuna ukuziphonsa imibuzo. Uphonsele uSoni inselelo ngakushilo. “Othi ngikusize ngomsebenzi wakho weSoni, kumele usize ikhomishini ithole iqiniso, hhayi ukuba uphushe imibono ethize. Akumele ungisabise, ngeke ngisabiseke,” kusho uMontana. USoni uthe ngeke ambuze uMontana uma esevele esethathe isinqumo esithize ngazokuphendula. Ngokwakhe uthe kumele athole ukuthi yini yena ayaziyo ngaleyo mibuzo. 